						            <ptr target="eiad-bibl:Parabrahma_Sastry1984"/>
					          </bibl> (with alternative readings supplied by the editor of
					the journal, marked Ed. in the apparatus). Re-edited here
					from published documentation. Autopsy of the boulder was
					unfortunately not very helpful.</p>
